<main class="">
  <el-form
    ref="formModel"
    label-width="60px"
    label-position="left"
    :model="formModel"
  >
    <el-form-item
      label="标题"
      :rules="[{required: true, trigger: 'blur', message: '标题为必填项'}]"
    >
      <el-input placeholder="标题"/>
    </el-form-item>
    <el-form-item
      label="类型"
      :rules="[{required: true, trigger: 'blur', message: '类型为必填项'}]"
    >
      <el-select
        v-model="selectValue"
        placeholder="请选择"
      >
        <el-option
          v-for="item in dictList"
          :key="item.dictCode"
          :value="item.dictCode"
          :label="item.dictValue"/>
      </el-select>
    </el-form-item>
    <el-form-item
      label="内容"
    >
      <MarkdownEditor v-model="markStr" height="500px"/>
    </el-form-item>
  </el-form>
</main>
